  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Empower 200 Poor Single Mothers In Rural Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;I intentionally cut my throat so I bleed to death because it was of no use living anymore&quot; said Ama, a 23-year young woman rescued from attempted suicide in July 2019. Sadly, Ama was abandoned by the father at age 3.  Her single mother couldn&apos;t provide for her daily subsistence.  So, she left home at age 12 to fend for herself.  Like her Mom, thousands of single mothers  in rural  Ghana struggle daily to care for their children due to poverty. You&apos;re their only hope; put a smile on their face.</narrative>
  </description>
